## Unit V — GitHub Actions

### Q14. Types of workflow triggers
- `push` — fires on code push to a branch
- `pull_request` — fires when a PR is opened or updated
- `schedule` — runs on a cron schedule
- `workflow_dispatch` — allows manual execution from the GitHub interface

