## Handy Command Reference

| Action | Command |
|--------|---------|
| Download image | `docker pull nginx:alpine` |
| Start detached container | `docker run -d --name webapp -p 8085:80 nginx` |
| Check logs | `docker logs webapp` |
| Open a shell | `docker exec -it webapp sh` |
| Stop and remove | `docker stop webapp; docker rm webapp` |
| Build an image | `docker build -t myapp:1.0 .` |
| Launch Compose stack | `docker compose up -d` |
| Run Maven build | `mvn clean verify` |

